column5: Located right off the toll road, you can get to Round Rock, Austin or Georgetown in about 5 minutes...restaurants and dining, family-friendly activities, nightlife all 5 minutes away as well.. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, business travelers, and families. Stone hill Shopping Center - less then 5 minutes away - Dicks Sporting, movie theater, Target, Wings n More, Sushi, Mexican, Russos,Best Buy. About 15 minutes from the Domain - Prime Shopping. 5 Minutes to Dell Diamond. F1
column8: Private,Clean Home in a beautiful subdivision
